description: Outline planning application (all matters reserved) for the mixed-use redevelopment of the existing Aberfeldy estate comprising: Demolition of 297 existing residential units and 1,990 sq m of non-residential floorspace and creation of a mixed-use scheme comprising new residential units (C3) in 15 blocks between 2 and 10 storeys in height, plus non-residential floorspace including retail (A1-A5) and community and cultural uses (D1), together with new and improved public open space and public realm and vehicular and cycle parking.
